    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to address common chassis resonance issues. The S54 breathes through six individual throttle bodies, providing exceptional throttle response and a linear power band. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains precise with recently refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain integrity and compression ratios remain within factory specifications, ensuring a visceral, analog performance profile.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
