    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, impressive shine, showing only the lightest signs of careful road use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seats with minimal wear and a fully functional infotainment suite. Mechanically, it is in robust health; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the dual-zone climate control remains ice-cold. It has been meticulously maintained with a documented service history and sits on a set of premium tires with significant tread remaining. This is a dependable, well-cared-for car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any necessary repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
