    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. The interior is super clean, and it\u2019s clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure right now! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
