      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the chassis has received a rear subframe reinforcement to address common structural fatigue, and the valve lash has been recently adjusted to factory specifications. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and neutral handling balance these cars are renowned for. While the aesthetics reflect a life enjoyed on the road, the mechanical drivetrain and structural integrity are prioritized for the discerning purist.",
